
OKAPI / DHCPCTL

Perl interface to 'omapi' DHCP server control functions.

Copyright 2004 Mark Jason Dominus and the trustees of the University
of Pennsylvania.  (Contact mjd@isc.upenn.edu.)

License is hereby granted for personal use and study of this code, but
unauthorized distribution is prohibited.

Installation instructions:

	gzip -dc DHCPCTL-0.07.tar.gz | tar xf -
		(if you haven't already)

	perl Makefile.PL
	make test

	make install
		(if all the tests passed)


Version 0.01 / 20040125

Initial revision.

